title: Salem's School for Girls (1973) KATE JACKSON

sources.title: Salem's School for Girls (1973) KATE JACKSON
sources.description:
Stars: Pamela Franklin, Kate Jackson, Cheryl Ladd 
Director: David Lowell Rich

When a young woman enrolls at Salem's School for Girls to investigate her sister's suicide, she finds herself battling a crazed cult! Watch for a young Cheryl Ladd (aka Cheryl Stoppelmoor) as Judy.
